quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  85,1,Mi woondirii kammu jom ɗate ngun
  85,2,O woondirii ñalawma podaaɗo o
  85,3,O woodarii kala ceediiɗo e kala ko seedaaɗo
  85,4,Huɗaama yimɓe Ukhduud-fettinɓe leydi petti mawɗi
  85,5,Yiite marnge kuɓɓam
  85,6,Tuma nde ɓe jooɗi e dow mannge
  85,7,Kamɓe koɓe mbaɗata ko goonɗinɓe ɓe koɓe seediiɓe
  85,8,ɓe njoftiraaki ɓe si wonah ɓe ngoonɗinii Alla tedduɗo jettaaɗo
  85,9,Ko Alla Woodani Laamu kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin. Alla ko Kattanɗo kala huunde
  85,10,ɓeen fawɓe e dow juulɓe rewɓe e worɓe fitina refti ɓe tuubaani woodaniiɓe lepte jahannama woodaniiɓe lepte cumooje
  85,11,ɓeen goonɗinɓe ngoolli golle lobbe woodaniiɓe Aljannaaji na ila ley mum caatli ko ɗuum woni malal manngal. @Corrected
  85,12,Pellet nanngannde joom ma ko sattunde
  85,13,Ko Kanko tigi fuɗɗata tagu O rutta mbo
  85,14,Ko Kanko woni Yaafatooɗo Giɗo
  85,15,Mbo arsi tedduɗo woodani. @Corrected
  85,16,Baɗoowo ko O welaa
  85,17,taw si arii e maaɗa Yewtere fii Muusaa
  85,18,Fir*awna e Samuud
  85,19,Accu yedduɓe ɓe ngoni ko e fennude
  85,20,Alla na fiiltariiɓe caggal
  85,21,Kammbo ko mbo Quraana tedduɗo
  85,22,Hombo e alluwal deenangal